combine 
 - 170 g warm milk
 - 2 tsp sugar
 - 2 g yeast
rest 5 minutes 

whisk in
 - 1 egg
 - 45 g oil
 - 1/4 tsp salt
 - 120 g flour
 - 1 tsp vanilla extract 
rest covered for 1 hour
use now or refrigerate overnight

use 3/4 cup scrapped per waffle
use 1 cup batter for denser results ( Julien )

set iron to 200C
brush iron with oil just before every cook

reheat from room temperature in 200C iron for 45 seconds

#dessert
#breakfast
